### BIG IDEA

**"Consistency is the missing variable, the 3+3 rotation closes the gap between wearing and learning."**

The core insight: 1 pair works as a trial but creates a learning interruption every time it hits the laundry. The 3+3 isn't just "more pairs", it's an unbroken feedback loop. The creative approach frames the 3+3 as the mechanism partner to the Body-Signal Learning Layer, not as a bulk discount.

