| Level | Required Ratio | Delivered | Notes |
|-------|---------------|-----------|-------|
| **L1** | 70/30 | ✅ | Pre-K context implied (30 days, consistency), urgency on pricing is gentle but present. |
| **L2** | 40/60 | ✅ | Mechanism depth (rotation = data stream), testimonial L2-specific ("4 years of tries"), practical framing. |
| **L3** | 20/80 | ✅ | Zero urgency on CTA. Soft secondary option. Testimony from Level 3 parent ("not trained yet. But he paused."). |
| **GF** | 50/50 | ✅ | "Whether...Or...If..." opener covers all sub-groups (diagnostic entrants, label-rejecters, sensory-difference, overwhelmed). Three-Family pattern lets each sub-group self-identify. |

